<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<key>UIApplicationSceneManifest</key>
	<dict>
		<key>UIApplicationSupportsMultipleScenes</key>
		<false/>
		<key>UISceneConfigurations</key>
		<dict>
			<key>UIWindowSceneSessionRoleApplication</key>
			<array>
				<dict>
					<key>UISceneConfigurationName</key>
					<string>Default Configuration</string>
					<key>UISceneDelegateClassName</key>
					<string>$(PRODUCT_MODULE_NAME).SceneDelegate</string>
				</dict>
			</array>
		</dict>
	</dict>
	<key>UILaunchStoryboardName</key>
	<string>LaunchScreen</string>
	<key>UIRequiresFullScreen</key>
	<true/>
	<key>KAKAO_NATIVE_APP_KEY</key>
	<string>$(KAKAO_NATIVE_APP_KEY)</string>
	<key>DATA_GO_KR_SERVICE_KEY</key>
	<string>$(DATA_GO_KR_SERVICE_KEY)</string>
	<key>KAKAO_REST_API_KEY</key>
	<string>$(KAKAO_REST_API_KEY)</string>
	<key>NAVER_CLIENT_ID</key>
	<string>$(NAVER_CLIENT_ID)</string>
	<key>NAVER_CLIENT_SECRET</key>
	<string>$(NAVER_CLIENT_SECRET)</string>
	<key>CFBundleURLTypes</key>
	<array>
		<dict>
			<key>CFBundleURLSchemes</key>
			<array>
				<string>kakao$(KAKAO_NATIVE_APP_KEY)</string>
			</array>
		</dict>
	</array>
	<key>LSApplicationQueriesSchemes</key>
	<array>
		<string>kakaomap</string>
		<string>kakaokompassauth</string>
		<string>kakaotalk</string>
		<string>storekit</string>
	</array>
	<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>주변 강아지 유치원·호텔을 지도에서 찾기 위해 위치 정보가 필요합니다.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>주변 강아지 유치원·호텔을 지도에서 찾기 위해 위치 정보가 필요합니다.</string>
	<key>NSCalendarsUsageDescription</key>
	<string>예약이 확정되면 캘린더에 일정을 추가하기 위해 접근 권한이 필요합니다.</string>
	<key>NSCalendarsFullAccessUsageDescription</key>
	<string>예약이 확정되면 캘린더에 일정을 추가하고, 예약 취소 시 해당 일정을 삭제하기 위해 접근 권한이 필요합니다.</string>
</dict>
</plist>
